   Issue: There's no route/controller method to cancel an approved/disbursed loan.
          The deleteLoan() method handles deletion but loan status 'Cancelled' is never
          set programmatically.
   Fix: Add a cancel() method and route.

G2. [MEDIUM] No Export Functionality for Installment Schedule
   Issue: The show page displays installments in HTML table but there's no PDF/Excel
          export option for the installment schedule.
   Fix: Add export buttons using Laravel Excel or DomPDF.

G3. [LOW] No Email/Notification on Status Change
   Issue: When a loan is approved/rejected/disbursed, the employee receives no
          notification.
   Fix: Dispatch notification events in approveLoan(), rejectLoan(), disburseLoan().

